udhr","tag-wealth-al-mal"],"aioseo_notices":[],"jetpack_featured_media_url":"","jetpack_shortlink":"https:\/\/wp.me\/p95VHY-2Du","jetpack_sharing_enabled":true,"jetpack-related-posts":[{"id":38092,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2022\/08\/11\/riba-decreases-akhirah\/","url_meta":{"origin":10136,"position":0},"title":"Hadith on Riba: Usury increases wealth, decreases rewards in Hereafter","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"August 11, 2022","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn Mas\u2019ud reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cNo one increases his wealth by usury except that his result will be little.\u201d Source: Sunan Ibn Ma\u0304jah 2279 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Albani \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0650 \u0627\u0628\u0652\u0646\u0650 \u0645\u064e\u0633\u0652\u0639\u064f\u0648\u062f\u064d \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0650 \u0627\u0644\u0646\u064e\u0651\u0628\u0650\u064a\u0650\u0651 \u0635\u064e\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0649 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0647\u064f \u0639\u064e\u0644\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0647\u0650 \u0648\u064e\u0633\u064e\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0645\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0645\u064e\u0627 \u0623\u064e\u062d\u064e\u062f\u064c \u0623\u064e\u0643\u0652\u062b\u064e\u0631\u064e\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":7503,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/10\/03\/disobedience-to-mothers\/","url_meta":{"origin":10136,"position":1},"title":"Hadith on Parents: Allah forbids disobedience to mothers","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"October 3, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Al-Mughirah ibn Sha\u2019bah reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cVerily, Allah has forbidden you from disobeying your mothers, withholding charity, demanding from others, and burying your daughters alive. Allah disapproves that you spread talebearing and gossip, ask many unnecessary questions, and waste your wealth.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":11993,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/02\/03\/riba-cursed\/","url_meta":{"origin":10136,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Riba: Allah curses all involved in usury","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"February 3, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Abdullah ibn Mas\u2019ud reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \"Allah has cursed the one who consumes usury, its client, its witness, and its recorder. Usury and adultery do not become widespread among people but that they will become vulnerable to the punishment of Allah Almighty.\" Source:\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":15292,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/07\/22\/extravagance-gold-silver-silk\/","url_meta":{"origin":10136,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Luxury: Prohibition of silk clothes, gold dishes","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"July 22, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Hudhayfah reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \"Do not drink from gold or silver vessels, and do not wear silk or brocade. Verily, these are for unbelievers in the world and for us in the Hereafter.\" Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 5633, S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 2067 Grade: Muttafaqun Alayhi\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":43264,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2025\/03\/19\/hadith-on-euphrates-trial-over-treasure-before-the-hour\/","url_meta":{"origin":10136,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Euphrates: Trial over treasure before the Hour","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"March 19, 2025","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cSoon the Euphrates River will disclose a treasure of gold. Whoever witnesses it, let him not take anything from it.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 7119, S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 2894 Grade: Muttafaqun Alayhi (authenticity agreed upon) according to Al-Bukhari\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":15295,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/07\/22\/haram-silver-gold-dishware\/","url_meta":{"origin":10136,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Extravagance: Silver and gold dishes, cutlery forbidden","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"July 22, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Umm Salamah reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cWhoever drinks from a vessel of gold or silver, surely he has only filled his belly with the fire of Hell.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 5634, S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 2065 Grade: Muttafaqun Alayhi (authenticity agreed upon) according to\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]}],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/10136","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/3712"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=10136"}],"version-history":[{"count":0,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/10136\/revisions"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=10136"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/categories?post=10136"},{"taxonomy":"post_tag","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/tags?post=10136"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https:\/\/api.w.org\/{rel}","templated":true}]}}